data.description: Section 8 welcome. Beautiful home in one of the most popular subdivision of Paloma creek in little Elm! Foyer on this gorgeous two story floor plan house takes you to an specious living space. Family room overlooks backyard and offers lots of windows to allows natural lights in. Kitchen features nice countertops, island, stainless appliances and breakfast area. All bedrooms are upstairs along with a bonus room, great for entertaining! Primary bedroom boasts an ensuite bath, dual sinks, garden tub, separate shower & walk-in closet. Large secondary bedrooms feature walk-in closets. Lots of storage throughout the home. Great community amenities include multiple pools, playgrounds, gyms, and miles of trails along the lake. Backyard will be perfect for summer time with nice patio.
